msgid """You command the Technician Cruiser Apollo, a repair ship on the border of \ndangerous space.\n\nThe Apollo is outfitted with minimal weapons as there is a cease-fire \nbetween the Human Navy and the neighboring Kraylor.\n\nYou are tasked with discovering the cause of damage on one of your deep \nspace telescopes.\n\nThis scenario is limited to one player ship: the Atlantis Apollo."""
